data.description: Beautiful 5 Bedroom 3.5 Bath Home with a Detached 2 Car Garrage,  located in Master Planned Community of Summerwood in the Edgewater Estates. Enjoy your covered back patio overlooking  Large backyard that  backs up to the Nature Reserve. Remodeled Kitchen with Large Island and Granite Counters. Large Living Room with Fireplace and Formal Dining area and breakfast room downstairs. Large Gameroom and 4 Bedrooms upstairs.  You will enjoy the neighborhood pools, workout facilities, and tennis courts, along with beautiful lakes with paved walking/riding paths and playgrounds for the kids.
